{"tid":2120160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門富臨酒家分店違反防疫規例遭食環署檢控","createTime":"2020-07-22T13:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T17:00:57.000Z","uid":64603,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d9fd6f9f2636d53feb0b2cf3b4db1c76fafed3","tid":2120160,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:27:13.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】屯門中央廣場富臨酒家累計十多人感染新冠病毒。食環署表示，早前派員到場巡查時，發現酒家未有按照規例實行防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n有關的酒樓已經暫停營業。食環署表示，周一派員到酒樓巡查，發現店內有員工在處理食物時，未有按規定佩戴口罩，餐桌之間少於1.5米間距，亦沒有有效分隔，涉嫌違反規管餐飲業的規例，已向業務負責人提出檢控，並敦促他們參照建議，停業清潔及消毒，署方會繼續留意其情況及跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=398981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398981&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=ec0567c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D398981&h=fa43c038\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=398981</a>"},{"pid":"60b44a3374103269384790dc510813d36fa48ac4","tid":2120160,"uid":207280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743eee2868a386d6634ef364d5cc8717512da47c","tid":2120160,"uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-11-2020/BOB8sL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-11-2020%2FBOB8sL.gif&h=4e1e51f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66da9b003db5ed20464c8df5a9e2119fa2162d79","tid":2120160,"uid":30836,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T13:47:25.000Z","msg":"爆咗先檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass